company_name: HABEMA FUTTERMITTEL GMBH & CO. KG PRODUKTIONS- UND UMSCHLAGSGESELLSCHAFT
information: The company HABEMA FUTTERMITTEL GMBH & CO. KG PRODUKTIONS- UND UMSCHLAGSGESELLSCHAFT, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1994, which operates in the Feeds for animal farming industry. It is based in Hamburg, Germany.
